            "answer": "<p>A complete body care routine includes cleansing, treating, and moisturizing to keep skin feeling healthy and balanced. Start with a <a href=\"/collections/body-wash\" title=\"Vegan Body Wash\">body wash</a> to gently cleanse, follow with targeted treatments like <a href=\"/products/bacne-warrior-acne-fighting-body-spray\" title=\"Bacne Warrior Acne Fighting Body Spray\">Bacne Warrior Acne Fighting Body Spray</a>, and finish with a nourishing <a href=\"/collections/body-lotion\" title=\"Vegan Lotions & Creams\">body lotion</a> to hydrate and soften skin. Explore the full bath and body range from Pacifica Beauty for a complete self-care routine.</p>"
          }
        },
